    subtitle: 'Our refund policy and your statutory right of withdrawal (Widerrufsbelehrung) under German law.',
    intro: 'This policy describes the conditions under which we provide refunds and your statutory right of withdrawal under German law. For business customers (B2B), only our internal refund policies apply. For consumers (B2C - private persons using the service for purposes outside their professional activity), the statutory right of withdrawal under \u00a7\u00a7 312g, 355 BGB also applies.',
